{"tid":1349101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到文宣睇] 除左元朗同開槍 記得宣傳埋宣言同臨時立法會","createTime":"2019-07-22T09:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:13:03.000Z","uid":278201,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5c071aff756fe4be88002d07a37756b41cdf15","tid":1349101,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:36:16.000Z","msg":"重開加改好標題 多謝少林詩人絲打提點<br />\nSorry for p牌仔<br />\n係咁多cam面前讀左宣言，唔排除成立臨時立法會完全冇人提過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣加多項呀唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406559c096532513e468ada2830e3140c44b3776","tid":1349101,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5ec9da5c6bb617f0c6fed5bacc2f5aee59001f9a","tid":1349101,"uid":73893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bdfa1f0d317368cb0faf740eb419c897020f232a","tid":1349101,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:39:29.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"031684dae07c0dcf55cc64fe1f6759c4840ec19e","tid":1349101,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:41:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e2f3f40c86a1c4af4565c4a13006fd6cbb76f8c","tid":1349101,"uid":144237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e8be057780053522a414a69f4e168014cfe6b56","tid":1349101,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:44:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8308a6a1ea889c5bc574e069a076b3c25fa23e9c","tid":1349101,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"